AI-Powered Incident Response  - RCA Summary  

We built an end-to-end AI SRE automation pipeline on AWS using Amazon Web Services.

The goal of this lab:

When EC2 CPU goes high → CloudWatch triggers alarm → Lambda calls AI model → AI generates RCA report → Email with incident + remediation is sent automatically.
This simulates a real SRE incident auto-response system.

